# NAME

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_changefullname - Change full name for a posix account of a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_posixaccount\_changefullname *username* *fullname*

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to change the full name (aka Gecos field) of a posix account.

# EXAMPLES

	schoolmesh_posixaccount_changefullname john "John Doe"

